name: #04 - BLACK - CMYK SERIES
description:
The CMYK Series of popsicles were inspired by the moment of finding a Digital Video Cassette hidden by time and then spontaneously discovered. This pop is the flavor of modernized nostalgia created from the typography, color, texture, and sound.

The CMYK Series is the first series of Neon Popsicles created by @LowRes_4tw in collaboration with @Horchatacluuub for music.
